sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant V as Viewer Count Service
    participant K as Kafka
    participant R as Redis

    Note over U,R: 1. Heartbeat
    loop every 30s
        U->>V: POST /streams/{streamId}/heartbeat {userId}
        V->>V: validate JWT token
        V->>K: publish ViewerHeartbeat {streamId, userId}
        K->>V: consume ViewerHeartbeat
        V->>R: SETEX viewer:{userId} 60
    end

    Note over V,R: 2. Ghost User
    R->>V: EXPIRED viewer:{userId}
    V->>R: SISMEMBER viewers {userId}
    R-->>V: 1 or 0
    alt exists
        V->>R: SREM viewers {userId}
        V->>R: DECR viewer_count
    else already removed
        Note over V: Ignore
    end